    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Stage 3 of Grafvitnir's manifestation — the Rot-hunger is no longer constrained by physical shape. It is a formless, reality-bending void of hunger that can only be defeated by Kaelen's willing presence at the Green Heart and a 4-round counter mechanism while the party survives. World-Ending Swipe reaches across the entire battlefield, Despair Made Flesh corrodes will and Hit Points alike, and Root Storm fills the air with corruption-laced debris. 150 Hit Points, Titanic. Two turns per round. This is the end of everything, or the beginning of restoration.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
